data.description: Welcome to 4364 Millen Ln, a charming home located at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac. This spacious property boasts 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing plenty of room for a growing family.    With 1340 square feet of living space on .35 acres, there is plenty of room to spread out and make this house your own. The large backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor entertainment and activities.    Although this home is ready for a family to move in, it could use some personal touches and love making it your own. The potential is endless with this property, allowing you to make it truly your dream home.    In addition to all of these great features, it also includes a convenient 2 car garage, providing ample storage space for vehicles and other belongings.    Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home. Come see it today and envision the endless possibilities that await you!
